      "    *   **Table (Center):** Top 10 `Customers` (by `CustomerID`) by `Total Sales Revenue`, `Total Quantity Sold`, `Number of Transactions`. (Identify high-value customers).\n",
      "    *   **Line Chart (Bottom Left):** `Number of Unique Customers` by `Month` (from `Dim_Date`). (Customer acquisition/retention trend).\n",
      "    *   **Tree Map (Right):** `Total Sales Revenue` by `Product` with size representing `Sales Revenue` and color representing `Average Unit Price`. (Visualizing product sales and pricing at a glance).\n",
